VI am a computer science and engineering professor here at Carnegie Mellon,
p4
aVand my research focuses on usable privacy and security,
p5
aVand so my friends like to give me examples
p6
aVof their frustrations with computing systems,
p7
aVespecially frustrations related to
p8
aVunusable privacy and security.
